    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-style:italic\"><em>You blast nearby creatures with magical and extremely loud noise.</em></span></p><p class=\"font_8\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold\"><strong>Action</strong></span> - 20 ft. Cone - Magical - 1 Round</p><p class=\"font_8\">You expend a @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.kg7VBahhFH6gDFIh]{bardic inspiration} die to use this ability.</p><p class=\"font_8\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold\"><strong>Constitution</strong></span> <strong>Save</strong> (DC Equal to Bard Spells)</p><ul class=\"font_8\"><li><p><strong>Failure</strong>: &amp;reference[thunder] damage equal to three rolls of your @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.kg7VBahhFH6gDFIh]{bardic inspiration} die and target is &amp;reference[deafened].</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul>",
      "chat": "<p><span style=\"font-weight:bold\"><strong>Action</strong></span> - 20 ft. Cone - Magical - 1 Round</p><p class=\"font_8\">You expend a @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.kg7VBahhFH6gDFIh]{bardic inspiration} die to use this ability.</p><p class=\"font_8\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold\"><strong>Constitution</strong></span> Save (DC Equal to Bard Spells)</p><ul class=\"font_8\"><li><p class=\"font_8\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold\"><strong>Failure</strong></span>: sonic damage equal to three rolls of your @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.kg7VBahhFH6gDFIh]{bardic inspiration} die and target is &amp;reference[deafened].</p></li><li><p class=\"font_8\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold\"><strong>Success</strong></span>: Half damage.</p></li></ul>"
